transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan Shri Krishna Traders mein baat ho rahi hai Kushal Goyal ji se?
Executive: Ji ji.
Customer: Very good morning sir, main Asim Khan baat kar raha tha Indiamart.com se business manager. Aapki company registered hai Indiamart ke sath mein sir.
Executive: Ji ji main wo karta hu, main aapko back call kar lijiyega, main abhi line pe aaya hu.
Executive: Achcha achcha okay theek hai.
